Dialogue: 1,0:01:03.22,0:01:04.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:04.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ah
Dialogue: 1,0:01:04.07,0:01:08.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又是裤头村水母田美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.07,0:01:05.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,another beautiful day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:08.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in Bikini Bottom's own Jellyfish Fields
Dialogue: 1,0:01:08.95,0:01:12.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好一个天然淳朴的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.95,0:01:12.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,an untamed world of natural order
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.46,0:01:11.34,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1130,444)}水母田\N母口数 四百万
Dialogue: 1,0:01:12.20,0:01:14.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小水母们在此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:14.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,where the little jellyfish jellies
Dialogue: 1,0:01:14.37,0:01:17.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,畅游于海景之间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.37,0:01:17.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,roam free across the salty seascape
Dialogue: 1,0:01:17.61,0:01:19.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但凡有水母的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.61,0:01:19.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And where there is jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:01:19.75,0:01:21.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就会有水母捕手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.75,0:01:21.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,there is the jellyfish hunter
Dialogue: 1,0:01:25.62,0:01:27.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是我今天捉到的第十二只
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.62,0:01:27.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're my 12th catch of the day
Dialogue: 1,0:01:27.47,0:01:29.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要叫你小十二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.47,0:01:29.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to call you Twelvy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.98,0:01:31.65,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(402,826)}水母酱
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.02,0:01:31.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我挠我挠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.02,0:01:31.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kitchy-kitchy-koo
Dialogue: 1,0:01:35.35,0:01:36.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  小十二
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.35,0:01:36.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, Twelvy
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.25,0:01:43.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.25,0:01:43.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's you
Dialogue: 1,0:01:57.97,0:02:01.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们又见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.97,0:02:01.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just you and me again
Dialogue: 1,0:02:01.15,0:02:05.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,田里水母我都至少捉过还取名过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.15,0:02:03.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've caught and named every jellyfish
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:05.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in this field at least once
Dialogue: 1,0:02:05.87,0:02:09.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除了你  无名氏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:09.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,except you, No-name
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:11.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fn宋体\pos(782.667,1024)\3c&H998732&\bord4\be3}放马过来啊
Dialogue: 1,0:02:56.03,0:02:56.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,捉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.03,0:02:56.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.17,0:03:01.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真见鬼  怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.17,0:03:01.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Barnacles, how did he do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.25,0:03:05.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总有一天我会捉到无名氏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:05.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Some day I'll catch ol' No-name
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.54,0:03:07.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(440,478)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:03:06.25,0:03:07.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要吃午饭了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.25,0:03:07.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going on my lunch break, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.17,0:03:09.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最多只能吃五分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:09.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got five minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:03:10.97,0:03:12.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比昨天还多了一分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:12.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One more minute than yesterday
Dialogue: 1,0:03:13.07,0:03:15.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝准备发射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:15.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob ready for launch
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.22,0:03:21.97,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(646,660)}水母酱
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.60,0:03:29.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:29.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yum
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.19,0:03:33.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:33.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.95,0:03:39.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  那是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:39.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy, what the heck is that?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:39.25,0:03:41.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是个洞  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:41.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, this is a hole, good sir
Dialogue: 1,0:03:41.50,0:03:43.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我身为一个海绵  通常都
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:43.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see, I am a sponge, and we typically
Dialogue: 1,0:03:43.85,0:03:46.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是那东西  是那东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.85,0:03:46.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not that, that
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只是个蟹黄堡而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.00,0:03:47.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's just a little old Krabby Patty
Dialogue: 1,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,里面抹了水母酱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:49.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,smothered in jellyfish jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:03:49.92,0:03:53.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我叫它  水母酱蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:53.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I call it a "Krabby Patty with jellyfish jelly"
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.67,0:03:54.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以尝尝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.67,0:03:54.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Could I try some?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:54.72,0:03:55.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:55.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太神了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Amazing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.15,0:04:05.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定要广而告之
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:05.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got to tell someone about this
Dialogue: 1,0:04:06.76,0:04:07.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:07.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, all you people
Dialogue: 1,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, all you people
Dialogue: 1,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:10.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, all you people
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.70,0:04:14.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能不能听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:14.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,won't you listen to me?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:14.48,0:04:15.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我刚吃了个三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.48,0:04:15.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I just had a sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.86,0:04:17.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是一般的三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:17.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,no ordinary sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.25,0:04:21.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是加了水母酱的三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:21.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A sandwich filled with jellyfish jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:04:22.17,0:04:25.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老兄  一定要尝尝这个三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:25.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, man, you got to try this sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.82,0:04:28.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是一般的三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:28.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's no ordinary sandwich
Dialogue: 1,0:04:28.41,0:04:33.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是全海洋最好吃的三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:33.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the tastiest sandwich in the sea
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.16,0:04:39.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:39.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.88,0:04:41.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.13,0:04:43.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁又在放章鱼哥的唱片了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.13,0:04:43.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's playing Squidward's records again?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没人在放  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:45.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:45.00,0:04:47.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我只是在跟客人分享我的水母酱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.00,0:04:46.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I was just sharing my jellyfish jelly
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:47.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with the customers
Dialogue: 1,0:04:50.94,0:04:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拿去吃吧  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:52.00,0:04:54.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带你的味蕾来趟旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.00,0:04:54.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,send your taste buds on a journey
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.25,0:04:59.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,竟敢乱改我蟹黄堡的配方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.25,0:04:59.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Messin' with the patty's formula
Dialogue: 1,0:04:59.30,0:05:00.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那是叛变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:00.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's mutiny
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.76,0:05:01.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:01.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, I ought to
Dialogue: 1,0:05:01.68,0:05:04.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生  这是我吃过最好吃的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:04.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sir, this is the greatest thing I've ever eaten
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以后午餐我都来这边吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:06.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to come back here for lunch
Dialogue: 1,0:05:06.87,0:05:09.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,后半辈子每天都吃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.87,0:05:09.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,every day for the rest of my life
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.20,0:05:13.83,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(910,856)}钱
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.87,0:05:13.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,兄弟  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:13.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, buddy, you all right?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事吧  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:18.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You okay, Mr. K?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:18.72,0:05:21.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我给你安排一项任务
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:21.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, I got a proposition for you
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.89,0:05:23.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你去给我捉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:23.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's about you go catch me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:23.54,0:05:26.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,几只那种钱母过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:26.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,some of those little money fish?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:26.07,0:05:29.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  带薪捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:29.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, getting paid to jelly-fish
Dialogue: 1,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这可是我一生的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.55,0:05:31.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's my life's dream
Dialogue: 1,0:05:31.15,0:05:32.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你梦想不可能实现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.15,0:05:32.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, keep dreamin'--
Dialogue: 1,0:05:32.47,0:05:33.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只能空闲时间捉  不给工资
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.47,0:05:33.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this'll be on your time
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.64,0:05:34.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  老板
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:34.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, sir
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.64,0:05:36.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快去给我捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:36.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, go get me some jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.76,0:05:37.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,动作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.76,0:05:37.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and make it
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.87,0:05:39.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.87,0:05:39.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.35,0:05:42.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.47,0:05:43.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还得要再多点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.47,0:05:43.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're going to need more
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.59,0:05:45.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,单单一只水母可不够
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:45.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,than one puny jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.72,0:05:48.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可是老板  你要多少只水母
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:48.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But, sir, how many jellyfish do you need?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.50,0:05:50.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  整个生态系统里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:50.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, we have a whole ecosystem
Dialogue: 1,0:05:50.94,0:05:52.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都是饿肚子的金主顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:52.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,full of hungry payin' customers
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.95,0:05:53.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:53.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no
Dialogue: 1,0:05:54.27,0:05:55.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你该不会是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.27,0:05:55.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:55.20,0:05:58.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再也不为客人着想了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:58.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you've stopped carin' for the customers
Dialogue: 1,0:05:58.82,0:06:00.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:00.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, never
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.57,0:06:01.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就出去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:01.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then go out there
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.84,0:06:04.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我多捉水母过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:04.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and get me some more jellies
Dialogue: 1,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.62,0:06:07.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,务必要让水母舒服点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:07.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just make sure the jellyfish are comfortable
Dialogue: 1,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母都比较敏感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.30,0:06:09.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,they are all so sensitive
Dialogue: 1,0:06:09.92,0:06:12.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我会让水母舒服点的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:12.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll keep them comfortable all right
Dialogue: 1,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,舒服住进我钱包
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,inside me wallet
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:18.02,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(388,796)}水母田
Dialogue: 1,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母给你  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:27.03,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(784,818)}水母酱堡之家
Dialogue: 1,0:06:24.53,0:06:27.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还要再多点  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:27.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to need more than that, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多点水母  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:31.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More jellies, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:06:31.77,0:06:32.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.77,0:06:32.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll never do--
Dialogue: 1,0:06:32.42,0:06:33.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:33.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,more
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:33.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(606,656)}招租
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.39,0:06:40.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多点  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.39,0:06:40.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:06:47.25,0:06:50.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多这个字你是哪不懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:50.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What don't you understand about "more?"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.50,0:06:54.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.50,0:06:54.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More
Dialogue: 1,0:06:56.72,0:06:57.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:57.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.27,0:06:58.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:06:58.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More
Dialogue: 1,0:06:59.52,0:07:00.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:00.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.66,0:07:01.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.66,0:07:01.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More
Dialogue: 1,0:07:01.37,0:07:06.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,多点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.37,0:07:06.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,More
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(752,396)}水母田\N母口数 零
Dialogue: 1,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,已经没得捉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, there's no more
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.00,0:07:14.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这才叫捉水母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:14.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, that's jellyfishing
Dialogue: 1,0:07:29.85,0:07:33.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,感觉好像有谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:33.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It feels like somebody
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想给我推销东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.04,0:07:34.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wants to sell me something
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.65,0:07:42.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就跟你说他发现我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.65,0:07:42.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I told you he was on to us
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.07,0:07:56.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你推销的东西我都没兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.07,0:07:56.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in anything you're selling
Dialogue: 1,0:08:05.73,0:08:06.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的有种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:06.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It sure felt like
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一定是工作太勤奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:09.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I must be working too hard
Dialogue: 1,0:08:11.43,0:08:12.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我来接  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.43,0:08:12.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll get it, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂  海绵宝宝家
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, SpongeBob's house
Dialogue: 1,0:08:14.11,0:08:15.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:15.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob speaking
Dialogue: 1,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:17.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:25.22,0:08:26.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,打错了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.22,0:08:26.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A wrong number
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.82,0:08:34.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,估计是小蜗忘交电费了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:34.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess Gary forgot to pay the electric bill
Dialogue: 1,0:08:37.30,0:08:39.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗  是你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:39.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary, is that you?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.53,0:08:41.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:41.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gary?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.95,0:08:44.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:44.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好办法  小蜗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:45.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good idea, Gary
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,厨房里可能有蜡烛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's probably some candles in the kitchen
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.67,0:08:52.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哎哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.67,0:08:52.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 1,0:08:52.06,0:08:52.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.06,0:08:52.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what's this?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是怎么进来的  美食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:55.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you get in here, oh, delicious one?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:55.20,0:08:57.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃点小点心就不至于太紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.20,0:08:57.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little snack will calm my nerves
Dialogue: 1,0:08:57.94,0:09:01.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蓝水母酱蟹黄堡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:09:01.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A Krabby Patty with blue jelly
Dialogue: 1,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蓝水母
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:04.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blue jelly?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你好  无名氏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:07.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hello, No-name
Dialogue: 1,0:09:07.00,0:09:07.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:07.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what's happening?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:11.72,0:09:13.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无名氏  放我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.72,0:09:13.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No-name, let me out
Dialogue: 1,0:09:14.17,0:09:15.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你想拿我怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:15.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do with me?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.19,0:09:17.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:17.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,P-U
Dialogue: 1,0:09:17.27,0:09:19.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么怪味这么像大企业
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:19.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what smells like big business?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:20.17,0:09:21.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不记得有那家工厂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.17,0:09:21.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't remember that factory
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:24.91,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(668,794)}水母酱
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.91,0:09:46.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是什么可怕的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:46.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What is this horrible place?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我挠我挠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kitchy-kitchy-koo
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.90,0:09:58.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是怎样的怪物造就了这么个可怕场景
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:58.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What kind of monster is responsible for this horror?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:00.27,0:10:01.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  小的们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.27,0:10:01.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.60,0:10:04.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让特值钱的水母酱一直流下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:04.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,keep that gelatinous gold a-flowin'
Dialogue: 1,0:10:06.28,0:10:08.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.28,0:10:08.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:09.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:09.55,0:10:11.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我总算知道你为什么带我来这了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:11.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now I know why you brought me here
Dialogue: 1,0:10:11.77,0:10:12.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我们能怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.77,0:10:12.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But what can we do?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:18.68,0:10:19.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别再疯下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:19.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stops this madness
Dialogue: 1,0:10:19.97,0:10:21.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,马上停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.97,0:10:21.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stop it right now
Dialogue: 1,0:10:23.49,0:10:25.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,事情不是你看到的那样  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:25.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't what it looks like, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:25.85,0:10:26.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:26.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:10:26.46,0:10:27.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们只是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:27.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're just, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在开茶会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,having a little tea party
Dialogue: 1,0:10:31.20,0:10:32.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  茶会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.20,0:10:32.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, a tea party
Dialogue: 1,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你骗我  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You tricked me, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我本来不会把水母全捉来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have collected all those jellyfish
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.59,0:10:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要不是知道水母会有这种下场
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.59,0:10:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,had I known that this was their fate
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.30,0:10:41.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This isn't right
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.62,0:10:45.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母需要开阔的空间  还有新鲜的空气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:45.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,pJellyfish need wide open space and fresh air
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你别急  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.24,0:10:46.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Easy, boy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.50,0:10:47.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你拿那个想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:47.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,what are you doin' with that?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:48.10,0:10:52.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好久以前就该这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:52.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Something that should have been done a long time ago
Dialogue: 1,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:10:54.90,0:10:57.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,门上的螺栓吵得我好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.90,0:10:57.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The squeaky bolt on this door was driving me crazy
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.50,0:11:01.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  我要解放这些水母
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.50,0:11:01.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, I'm going to set these jellyfish free
Dialogue: 1,0:11:05.22,0:11:06.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你放不来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:06.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't--
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.52,0:11:08.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这门是声控的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:08.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the door is voice-activated
Dialogue: 1,0:11:08.10,0:11:11.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想让它开  只能等我说开
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:11.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it will only open if I say "open"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:14.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(926,356)}声控开关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:13.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(916,782)}关
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:14.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(916,782)}开
Dialogue: 1,0:11:16.31,0:11:18.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.31,0:11:18.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Freedom
Dialogue: 1,0:11:18.15,0:11:20.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:20.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Freedom
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.49,0:11:23.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们绝对抓不到我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.49,0:11:23.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll never catch me
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.08,0:11:28.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:28.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.72,0:11:32.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就不该盲目跟风健身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:32.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Blasted exercise craze
Dialogue: 1,0:11:41.02,0:11:43.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见了  朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.02,0:11:43.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good-bye, friends
Dialogue: 1,0:11:43.87,0:11:46.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以后不卖水母酱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:46.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm taking jelly off the menu
Dialogue: 1,0:11:47.42,0:11:49.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卖水母酱可把他给坑惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.42,0:11:49.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He really got burned on that deal
Dialogue: 1,0:11:51.12,0:11:52.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,本来就该这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:52.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All is as it should be
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.85,0:11:54.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我保证以后再也不用这张网了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:54.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I promise never to use this net
Dialogue: 1,0:11:54.98,0:11:57.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,除非是要做运动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:57.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for anything but pure sport again
Dialogue: 1,0:11:57.22,0:12:00.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水母从来就不应该让人抓走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:12:00.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Jellyfish aren't meant to be captured forever
Dialogue: 1,0:12:01.57,0:12:02.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,无名氏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.57,0:12:02.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, No-name
Dialogue: 1,0:12:03.25,0:12:05.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我现在应该可以给你取名了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:05.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I guess I can name you now
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要叫你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll call you
Dialogue: 1,0:12:07.72,0:12:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.72,0:12:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Friend
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:16.88,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(396,436)}厨师运动会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:21.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:19.25,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz19\pos(328,450)}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.72,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.27\pos(352,310)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz18.95\pos(314,342)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz21.2\pos(472,682)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.01,0:12:24.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 1,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,欢迎各位体育迷
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.55,0:12:27.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Welcome, sports fans
Dialogue: 1,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,观赏第21届
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.40,0:12:28.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the 21st
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.37,0:12:30.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村年度厨师运动会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:30.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Annual Bikini Bottom Fry Cook Games
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.19,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(390,322)}快餐体育场
Dialogue: 1,0:12:42.94,0:12:45.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我宣布厨师运动会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:45.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I declare these Fry Cook Games
Dialogue: 1,0:12:45.52,0:12:47.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开幕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:47.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,open
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,请稍候
Dialogue: 1,0:12:59.35,0:13:01.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我宣布厨师运动会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:01.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I declare these Fry Cook Games
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.87,0:13:03.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,开幕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.87,0:13:03.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,open
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.01,0:13:10.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第21届厨师运动会正式开幕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:10.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So begin the 21st Fry Cook Games
Dialogue: 1,0:13:10.41,0:13:12.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是个写实风鱼头
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:12.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm a realistic fish head
Dialogue: 1,0:13:12.49,0:13:16.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村快餐体育场天气晴好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.49,0:13:13.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it's a beautiful day
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:16.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,here at Bikini Bottom's Fast Food Coliseum
Dialogue: 1,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,各地运动员纷至沓来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They come from everywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,微波炉的嗡嗡声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:20.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,microwaves hum
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.57,0:13:22.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,肉饼的滋滋声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:22.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,patties sizzle
Dialogue: 1,0:13:24.92,0:13:30.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以及保温灯  让快餐精神又温又潮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:30.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and heat lamps keep the fast food spirit warm and soggy
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.92,0:13:33.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但本次的焦点在于一场激烈竞争
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:33.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But the real story is the bitter rivalry
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.45,0:13:35.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,竞争双方是两位前任参赛者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:35.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,between former competitors
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.02,0:13:37.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王的蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.02,0:13:37.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs of The Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:13:37.04,0:13:39.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,以及海之霸的痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:39.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and Plankton, of the Chum Bucket
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.29,0:13:40.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁会忘记当年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:40.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who could forget the year
Dialogue: 1,0:13:40.94,0:13:44.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板在五百腌椰菜级举重一举夺魁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:44.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs won gold for this 500-pickle clean and jerk?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.47,0:13:47.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正痞老板没放心上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.47,0:13:47.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:13:49.72,0:13:52.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是当年痞老板打动众多观众的壮举
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:52.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or when Plankton won the hearts of millions
Dialogue: 1,0:13:52.53,0:13:56.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美完成全套洋葱圈体操动作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:56.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by performing this perfect onion ring routine
Dialogue: 1,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,即便断了一根触角也在坚持
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with a broken antenna?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正蟹老板并不感动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs wasn't moved
Dialogue: 1,0:14:05.19,0:14:08.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最新消息称  今年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:08.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, late word is that this year
Dialogue: 1,0:14:08.10,0:14:11.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,将有一位新人代表蟹堡王参赛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.10,0:14:10.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Krusty Krab will be represented
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.03,0:14:11.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,by a new competitor
Dialogue: 1,0:14:11.66,0:14:15.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天可能将是他青春中最美好的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.66,0:14:15.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,on what is perhaps the greatest day of his young life
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.26,0:14:17.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天可能是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:17.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is perhaps
Dialogue: 1,0:14:17.30,0:14:19.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我青春中最美好的一天  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.30,0:14:19.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the greatest day of my young life, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我居然会代表蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:23.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe I'm representing the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.70,0:14:24.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,参加厨师运动会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:24.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in the Fry Cook Games
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.27,0:14:28.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能够摘金  就能取得荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.27,0:14:28.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,To bring home the gold is to bring honor and glory
Dialogue: 1,0:14:28.67,0:14:30.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带给蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.67,0:14:30.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:14:30.20,0:14:33.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,进而免费宣传  吸引顾客
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.20,0:14:33.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And all that free publicity will bring in customers
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.94,0:14:35.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,千万不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:35.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So don't lose
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,遵命  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:37.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.57,0:14:38.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:38.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty-Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:14:38.87,0:14:40.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:40.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty-Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty-Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.45,0:14:41.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:41.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty-Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.87,0:14:42.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:42.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.10,0:14:43.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,嗨  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:43.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:43.92,0:14:45.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:45.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty-Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:14:45.25,0:14:46.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.25,0:14:46.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty-Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:47.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty-Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:14:49.10,0:14:51.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是要挪动大地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.10,0:14:51.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to move the ground?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:51.52,0:14:53.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你那样挪不动的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.52,0:14:53.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll never move it like that
Dialogue: 1,0:14:53.24,0:14:54.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,必须要从地下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.24,0:14:54.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You got to get under
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,入手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,neath it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.13,0:14:56.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,搞什么  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:56.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:14:56.90,0:14:58.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是在为运动会做训练
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:58.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to train for the Games
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:58.62,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(738,920)}游  戏
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.62,0:14:59.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.62,0:14:59.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Games?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.54,0:15:00.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我能玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:00.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can I play?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:00.92,0:15:01.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抱歉  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.92,0:15:01.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.75,0:15:03.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你必须先当上厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.75,0:15:03.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you have to be a fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:15:03.67,0:15:04.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当上厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:04.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Be a fry cook?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is that all I gotta do?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.20,0:15:07.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:07.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That'll be easy
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.63,0:15:09.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你说简单是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.63,0:15:09.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "easy"?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.12,0:15:12.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这有什么难的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.12,0:15:12.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How hard can it be?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:12.22,0:15:15.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是随便什么人都可以当得上厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.22,0:15:15.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They don't let just anybody be a fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:15:15.20,0:15:16.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可是精英部队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:16.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're an elite corps
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.03,0:15:17.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:17.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on--
Dialogue: 1,0:15:17.88,0:15:20.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你就只是翻个肉饼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:20.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you're just flipping patties
Dialogue: 1,0:15:20.93,0:15:22.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,翻这个动作可没那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:22.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Flipping is not as easy as it sounds
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是回家去吧  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:27.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Why don't you go home, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:27.75,0:15:28.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你可以去参加
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:28.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can compete in
Dialogue: 1,0:15:28.72,0:15:31.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,躺石头地下一整天运动会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:31.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Laying-Under-A-Rock-All-Day Games
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.86,0:15:34.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码我不会抹指甲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.86,0:15:34.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least I don't polish my fingernails
Dialogue: 1,0:15:34.99,0:15:36.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把话收回去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:36.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You take that back
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.99,0:15:38.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,指甲指甲指甲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:38.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fingernails, fingernails, fingernails
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.90,0:15:40.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你连指甲都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:40.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't even have fingernails
Dialogue: 1,0:15:41.20,0:15:44.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信我听到的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.20,0:15:44.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I cannot believe what I am hearing
Dialogue: 1,0:15:44.52,0:15:46.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么可能听得见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.52,0:15:46.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How can you hear it?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.07,0:15:47.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还没耳朵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.07,0:15:47.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't have ears, either
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.62,0:15:49.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:49.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You
Dialogue: 1,0:15:49.58,0:15:51.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大洞  大洞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:51.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Holes, holes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,尖头
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.47,0:15:52.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cone-head
Dialogue: 1,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄块块
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:53.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yellow
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.05,0:15:53.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,粉星星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:53.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pink
Dialogue: 1,0:15:56.96,0:15:58.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要去找厨师工作去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.96,0:15:58.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get a job as a fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定会很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and it'll be easy
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fine
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.61,0:16:03.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:03.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty-Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.58,0:16:04.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:04.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty-Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:16:04.45,0:16:05.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:05.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krusty-Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:16:06.62,0:16:08.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,空气中弥漫着什么味道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.62,0:16:08.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's that smell in the air?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.63,0:16:12.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我闻到了痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:12.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I smell Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:16:14.48,0:16:15.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:15.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:15.90,0:16:17.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我味道可
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.90,0:16:17.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I smell
Dialogue: 1,0:16:19.40,0:16:20.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,味确实重
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:20.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's right
Dialogue: 1,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就爱捣乱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.32,0:16:33.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I love messing things up
Dialogue: 1,0:16:37.14,0:16:40.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好要决一死战了吗  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:40.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are you ready to do or die, Krabs?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:40.17,0:16:42.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向来都准备好了  痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.17,0:16:42.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Always ready, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.40,0:16:43.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,always ready
Dialogue: 1,0:16:44.07,0:16:46.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很好  因为今天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:46.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good, because today
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.97,0:16:50.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海之霸要把你打得
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:50.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Chumbucket is going to kick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.19,0:16:54.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:54.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,your carapace
Dialogue: 1,0:16:54.01,0:16:56.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,自以为是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:56.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what you think
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.10,0:16:57.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我手上还有位冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.10,0:16:57.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I got me a champion--
Dialogue: 1,0:16:57.90,0:16:59.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:16:59.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.15,0:17:00.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,露一手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:00.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Show him
Dialogue: 1,0:17:06.58,0:17:07.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:07.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look at him
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.86,0:17:09.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,状态绝佳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:09.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,in his prime
Dialogue: 1,0:17:09.37,0:17:10.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你绝对没机会赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:10.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You ain't got no chance
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.85,0:17:13.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你错就错在这里  老螃蟹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.85,0:17:13.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's where you're wrong, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.15,0:17:15.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,因为我  也有个冠军
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:15.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for I, too, have a champion
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.51,0:17:21.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,女士们先生们  全体目光
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:21.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ladies and gentlemen, turn your attention
Dialogue: 1,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,向西南侧通道看齐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.56,0:17:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to the southwest corridor
Dialogue: 1,0:17:25.28,0:17:26.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,另一边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.28,0:17:26.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Other way
Dialogue: 1,0:17:26.92,0:17:28.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,傻子一群
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:28.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Imbeciles
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.64,0:17:29.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:29.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And
Dialogue: 1,0:17:29.65,0:17:30.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别转了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:30.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,stop
Dialogue: 1,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:31.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,代表海之霸上场的这位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:33.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Representing the Chumbucket
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.90,0:17:37.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是个超级可怕超级恐怖的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:37.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a creature so fearsome, so terrible
Dialogue: 1,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,并且体积大得吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:40.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,so mind-bendingly large
Dialogue: 1,0:17:40.57,0:17:43.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可能会让场下某些体弱的观众
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.57,0:17:43.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that those of you with weak constitutions
Dialogue: 1,0:17:43.44,0:17:45.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怕得想逃出体育场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.44,0:17:45.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,may want to leave the stadium
Dialogue: 1,0:17:45.76,0:17:46.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:46.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I gotta get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.82,0:17:47.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.82,0:17:47.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too late
Dialogue: 1,0:17:47.67,0:17:50.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不管有没有准备好  他都要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:50.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ready or not, here he comes
Dialogue: 1,0:17:50.27,0:17:52.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,害怕吧颤抖吧  愚蠢的凡人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.27,0:17:52.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Quake with fear, you mortal fools
Dialogue: 1,0:17:53.30,0:17:56.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,请大家鞠躬致敬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:56.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bow down before the awesome might of
Dialogue: 1,0:17:59.77,0:18:02.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个大个子背上的才是真正的参赛者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.77,0:18:02.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this huge guy who's carrying the real contestant
Dialogue: 1,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.35,0:18:04.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick Star
Dialogue: 1,0:18:05.87,0:18:07.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  你来这干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.87,0:18:07.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:07.40,0:18:08.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又不是厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:08.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're not a fry cook
Dialogue: 1,0:18:08.62,0:18:13.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我当然是了  优秀宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:13.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am Mr. SpongeBob-Superior Pants
Dialogue: 1,0:18:13.17,0:18:14.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.17,0:18:14.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Check it out
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:17.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(410,376)}海之霸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.23,0:18:17.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(794,836)}派大星
Dialogue: 1,0:18:14.25,0:18:15.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经给海之霸工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:15.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I been working for the Chumbucket
Dialogue: 1,0:18:15.97,0:18:17.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,差不多有五分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.97,0:18:17.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for almost five minutes
Dialogue: 1,0:18:17.76,0:18:19.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那也没什么大不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:19.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, it doesn't matter anyway
Dialogue: 1,0:18:19.35,0:18:20.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,反正你快输到去喝西北风了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.35,0:18:20.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,'cause you're going to eat my dust
Dialogue: 1,0:18:21.89,0:18:23.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要喝也是喝我自己的西北风
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:23.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm eating my own dust
Dialogue: 1,0:18:23.42,0:18:24.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那也得我先
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.42,0:18:24.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not if I eat it first
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.80,0:18:25.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄块块
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.80,0:18:25.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yellow
Dialogue: 1,0:18:25.50,0:18:26.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,粉星星
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.50,0:18:26.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pink
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't believe it, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:18:29.42,0:18:32.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星明明还是我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:32.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought Patrick was my friend
Dialogue: 1,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Friend?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:33.02,0:18:34.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这边就不是了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.02,0:18:34.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not in here he ain't
Dialogue: 1,0:18:34.67,0:18:35.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:35.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.63,0:18:38.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他只是表面朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.63,0:18:38.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not really your friend
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.17,0:18:38.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:38.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:38.97,0:18:42.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他现在就在计划打垮你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.97,0:18:42.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's plotting your downfall right now
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.01,0:18:43.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.01,0:18:43.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He is?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:43.10,0:18:45.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他要在背后捅你刀子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:45.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's going to stab you in the back
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.93,0:18:47.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.93,0:18:47.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't
Dialogue: 1,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,当然可能了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course he would
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.95,0:18:50.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你看人家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.95,0:18:50.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just look at him
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,方块
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Square
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.12,0:18:54.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶魔的形状
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:54.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the shape of evil
Dialogue: 1,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那完全是对你职业技能的大不敬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.40,0:18:56.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a mockery of your profession
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.60,0:18:58.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,难道要眼睁睁看着个冒牌厨师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:58.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Are we going to let some pretender
Dialogue: 1,0:18:58.37,0:19:00.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,抢走本该属于蟹堡王的荣耀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.37,0:19:00.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,take away what belongs to the Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:19:00.74,0:19:01.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.74,0:19:01.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.87,0:19:02.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就强势起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:02.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Then get mean
Dialogue: 1,0:19:02.99,0:19:04.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很强势
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:04.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm mean
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愤怒起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:05.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get angry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:05.50,0:19:07.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我很愤怒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.50,0:19:07.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm angry
Dialogue: 1,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在上场
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:08.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get out there
Dialogue: 1,0:19:08.83,0:19:10.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,赢得
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.83,0:19:10.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And win
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.15,0:19:10.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:10.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That
Dialogue: 1,0:19:10.77,0:19:11.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奖牌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:11.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Medal
Dialogue: 1,0:19:22.02,0:19:23.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第一项赛事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:23.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Our first event
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:26.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1122,842)}油炸王
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.99,0:19:26.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,油锅撑杆跳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:26.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the deep-fry pole vault
Dialogue: 1,0:19:26.47,0:19:28.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为蟹堡王赢得比赛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:28.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Win this one for the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:19:28.67,0:19:32.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:32.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For the Krusty Krab
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.91,0:19:41.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我叫你赢  你就必须赢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:41.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Win this one because I told you to
Dialogue: 1,0:19:41.35,0:19:43.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你叫我必须赢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.35,0:19:43.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Because you told me to
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.79,0:19:48.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,炸鱼条
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:48.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fish sticks
Dialogue: 1,0:19:48.65,0:19:50.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来买炸鱼条
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.65,0:19:50.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get your fish sticks here
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.37,0:19:50.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(572,780)}炸鱼条
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,第二项赛事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.46,0:19:51.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The next event
Dialogue: 1,0:19:51.80,0:19:53.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,巧克力跳水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.80,0:19:53.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the chocolate high-dive
Dialogue: 1,0:19:54.12,0:19:56.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给正牌厨师让个道  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.12,0:19:56.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Make way for the real fry cook, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:19:57.40,0:20:00.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这次跳水  海绵宝宝将要尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.40,0:20:00.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For his dive, SpongeBob will be attempting
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.30,0:20:03.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,双棍香蕉软巧克力糖冰棍跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:03.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a full banana fudge-pop with two sticks
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.30,0:20:07.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在  一片寂静
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.30,0:20:07.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And now, absolute silence
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.32,0:20:09.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,激灵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:09.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I scream
Dialogue: 1,0:20:09.93,0:20:13.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,为了冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:13.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for ice cream
Dialogue: 1,0:20:16.11,0:20:17.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美入水
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:17.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect entry
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.72,0:20:19.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还裹上了烤杏仁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.72,0:20:19.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And toasted almonds--
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.45,0:20:20.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,意想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:20.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,that's unexpected
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.52,0:20:21.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他站稳了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.52,0:20:21.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He stuck it
Dialogue: 1,0:20:21.92,0:20:24.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看他裹得多均匀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:24.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And just look at that even coating
Dialogue: 1,0:20:25.95,0:20:26.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,超越我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:26.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Top that
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.11,0:20:27.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,粉星星
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.11,0:20:27.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pinky
Dialogue: 1,0:20:28.72,0:20:30.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,杏仁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:30.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Almonds?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.40,0:20:32.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真该死  太有才华了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:32.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Curse him, that's good
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.41,0:20:34.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然而太高雅  场下大众未必欣赏得来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.41,0:20:34.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but perhaps a bit too highbrow for this crowd
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.95,0:20:37.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他自以为高人一等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:37.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He thinks he's better than them
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.22,0:20:39.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,高你一等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.22,0:20:39.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Better than you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快上台给人家瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:42.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now get up there and show him
Dialogue: 1,0:20:42.34,0:20:45.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,咱普通百姓会怎么做牛奶冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:45.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,how the common man prepares his frozen dairy treats
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.30,0:20:51.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星将要重拾旧爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.30,0:20:51.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick will be resurrecting an old favorite
Dialogue: 1,0:20:51.06,0:20:54.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,单筒草莓甜筒  蘸上巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:54.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the single-scoop strawberry cone with a chocolate dip
Dialogue: 1,0:20:57.19,0:20:59.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看他此般聚精会神
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.19,0:20:59.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just look at that concentration
Dialogue: 1,0:21:00.03,0:21:02.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,入水不是很行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.03,0:21:02.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A little shaky on that entry--
Dialogue: 1,0:21:02.07,0:21:04.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是看看那形体
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.07,0:21:04.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but just look at that form
Dialogue: 1,0:21:04.45,0:21:06.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接招吧  黄块块
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:06.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take that, Yellow Boy
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.37,0:21:08.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你迟早笑不出来  粉星星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:08.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Laugh while you can, Pinky
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.12,0:21:09.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比赛还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:09.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.32,0:21:10.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你自以为会那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:10.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what you think
Dialogue: 1,0:21:10.60,0:21:12.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,但是比赛还没结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.60,0:21:12.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it's not over yet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:13.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(678,476)}千磅番茄酱
Dialogue: 1,0:21:16.17,0:21:17.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比赛还没结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.17,0:21:17.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.70,0:21:20.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,双方比分持平  进入最后一项赛事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:20.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With the score tied, we go to our final event
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.10,0:21:21.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,面包摔跤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.10,0:21:21.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bun Wrestling
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.77,0:21:23.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁将会摘金呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.77,0:21:23.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who will take home the gold?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.76,0:21:25.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是蟹堡王的蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.76,0:21:25.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs of the Krusty Krab?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:25.97,0:21:28.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了  他叫你黄块块
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.97,0:21:28.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't forget, he called ye yellow
Dialogue: 1,0:21:32.27,0:21:34.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还是海之霸的痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.27,0:21:34.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or Plankton, of the Chumbucket?
Dialogue: 1,0:21:34.72,0:21:37.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别忘了  他叫你粉星星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.72,0:21:37.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't forget, he called you pink
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.84,0:22:10.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不管海之霸了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.84,0:22:10.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget the Chumbucket--
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.51,0:22:12.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这个是私人恩怨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.51,0:22:12.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,this is personal
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:24.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1032,238)}海之霸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:24.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\a3\pos(770,868)}派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.15,0:22:24.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\a3\pos(770,868)}大星
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.28,0:22:26.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:26.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.96,0:22:32.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的名字不叫  大星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.96,0:22:32.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,My name's not "Rick"
Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.05,0:22:38.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.05,0:22:38.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't like you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:39.21,0:22:40.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我更不喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.21,0:22:40.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't like you more
Dialogue: 1,0:22:40.55,0:22:42.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我从来不喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.55,0:22:42.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I never liked you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.10,0:22:44.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一千倍不喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.10,0:22:44.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I a thousand times never liked you
Dialogue: 1,0:22:44.42,0:22:45.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,粉星星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.42,0:22:45.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pink
Dialogue: 1,0:22:45.06,0:22:45.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄块块
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.06,0:22:45.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yellow
Dialogue: 1,0:22:53.82,0:22:55.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,黄的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.82,0:22:55.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yellow
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.89,0:22:57.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,粉的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.89,0:22:57.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pink?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.72,0:23:01.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你还在乎我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.72,0:23:01.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You do care
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.85,0:23:08.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起保证再也不要打架了  兄弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.85,0:23:08.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's promise never to fight again, buddy
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.80,0:23:10.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.80,0:23:10.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, pal
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.10,0:23:11.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.10,0:23:11.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,let's go home
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.25,0:23:17.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.25,0:23:17.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where you going?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.52,0:23:20.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回来拼个你死我活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.52,0:23:20.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get back here and kill each other
Dialogue: 1,0:23:20.42,0:23:22.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你是我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:22.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're my best friend ever
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.52,0:23:24.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你也是  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.52,0:23:24.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You, too, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:23:24.92,0:23:27.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我内裤刚买的时候还是白的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:27.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You know, these were white when I bought them
